{"tid":1728683,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解唔收集tg或者自製tg驅散班拆rb藍絲？","createTime":"2019-11-17T03:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T06:22:37.000Z","uid":18639,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"67b857c70b810d58fd3dd8420c5ff0ecc296f286","tid":1728683,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:35:46.000Z","msg":"一）畫面好睇。成日話唔想民鬥民，咁用催淚彈得喇掛？無直接傷害到藍絲，而且我地每日都食緊tg，班藍絲同popo都唔會出黎自打嘴巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二）比班藍絲試下食tg既味道。班藍絲一直離哂地無食過tg，聞過tg先會知有幾咁危險，先會擔心自己既身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三）若然班藍絲為左防tg而帶口罩或者防毒面具既話，咁佢地仲點分示威者同自己人？而同時佢地亦成為左自己口中既暴徒。到時個個帶防毒面具，班popo點樣拉人都唔知，隨時拉哂班藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed3021cff6666ee55f3440e6ee8a9b0bf61656d","tid":1728683,"uid":121095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"how"},{"pid":"caccedab0bb28027d30cbacbb7134ebd178c0436","tid":1728683,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時會唔會比D popo賴示威者放二惡英"},{"pid":"f7337b7f849d48f6b998bc1a0befbe2eb229f267","tid":1728683,"uid":18639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ed3021cff6666ee55f3440e6ee8a9b0bf61656d","tid":1728683,"uid":121095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"how"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:38:19.000Z","msg":"我記得之前有巴絲自製煙餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89018b4c90ef1339e0491673f60797f9a52fbf2","tid":1728683,"uid":136860,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"caccedab0bb28027d30cbacbb7134ebd178c0436","tid":1728683,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時會唔會比D popo賴示威者放二惡英"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:39:36.000Z","msg":"你唔放佢都已經賴緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee4846078231df8a2fc88483c24da77334bc1ec","tid":1728683,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>他們在打的是「中共政權保衛戰」，而你們僅僅是在打「香港生活方式保衛戰」</strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，<strong>第一就是分化</strong>，<strong>把勇武派、和理非派拆分</strong>，<strong>第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」</strong>，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後<strong>隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒</strong>。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，<strong>但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能</strong>，坦白說，<strong>還是太嫩</strong>。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是<strong>北京</strong>要製造的<strong>焦點轉移</strong>。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong>。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"d974607b43191a3abc19f7662131dedf001a445b","tid":1728683,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e89018b4c90ef1339e0491673f60797f9a52fbf2","tid":1728683,"uid":136860,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"caccedab0bb28027d30cbacbb7134ebd178c0436","tid":1728683,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時會唔會比D popo賴示威者放二惡英"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:39:36.000Z","msg":"你唔放佢都已經賴緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:40:35.000Z","msg":"如果係收集返黎既tg 果d係佢地既tg黎 佢可以點樣賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51fa1164f39dc3ea6aaca5421e50817067e85d3","tid":1728683,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:42:06.000Z","msg":"[文宣組入] 請唔好幫候選人做文宣！犯法仲會累人坐監！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728047/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728047/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5e027304ff3b79b370bfbad476707894dd7fc66d","tid":1728683,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefc953adcc17d8220025c3003fb788fe1fb1794","tid":1728683,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:43:46.000Z","msg":"on9仔講到好似好簡單咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d8e14a62fadceffcf018935f627f0cbb357f8b","tid":1728683,"uid":266676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci